query:
SELECT COUNT(*) as "count!"
                  FROM users u
                  INNER JOIN user_roles ur ON ur.user_id = u.id AND ur.tenant_id = u.tenant_id
                  INNER JOIN roles r ON r.id = ur.role_id
                  WHERE u.tenant_id = $1
                    AND u.status = 'active'
                    AND r.name = $2
                    AND u.id != $3
